<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Elisabeth von Hohenzollern, Burggräfin von Nürnberg und Gräfin von Württemberg</head><p>Der Rat gewährt Johann Röder trotz vergangener Untaten gegen Nürnberger bis Katharinentag vier Tage Geleit, um ihn anzuhören.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_347" id="172v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_347_r1l10">Frawn Elıſabeth Burggrefın ʒu <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l11"><expan>Grefin<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>vvırtemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> wıtıben </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_347_r1l12">Gnedıge fraw als vns eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> yecʒ <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von Johan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l13">Röders <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . 
<del rend="strikethrough">Nu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l14">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan></del> . Nu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> vormals <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> / daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l15">Johan Röder / Vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>manıgfeltıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> beſchedıgt hat on </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l16">ſchuld vnd on ſache . / wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wenn <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> Johan Röder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l17"><expan>hıeʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> ſand Kathreyn tag ſchıerıſt . ʒu vns gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l18"><expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wıl . ſo ſol er <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu eren . ʒu vnd von Vns für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l19">vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on geuerde vnd bey vns für <expan>all<ex>er</ex>meniklıch</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l20">vıer tag geleyt haben . ſo <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır ſein rede alſdenn <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l21">hören . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd wolgefallen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l22"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_347" id="172v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Frawn Elisabeth, burggrefin zu <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>grefin<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                            <expan>Wirtemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> witiben</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige fraw, als uns ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> yecz
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von Johan Röders
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Nu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> vormals <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>,
                        daz <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Johan Röder uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>manigfeltikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> beschedigt hat on schuld und on
                        sache; wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wenn
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Johan Röder
                            <expan>hiezwische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">sand Kathreyn tag schierist</q>25.11.1421</note>
</app> zu uns gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wil, so sol er <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu eren zu und von uns für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on geverde und bey uns für
                                <expan>all<ex>er</ex>meniklich</expan> vier tag geleyt haben, so
                                <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir sein rede alsdenn
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
